rows.label: tlk42100181_03_msg0002
rows.name:
It nighttime now. That mean Magomago
get to play with Grampypon! Magomago
sleepy-sleepy, but also happy-happy!

rows.label: tlk42100181_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Guess what? Grampypon make friends
with high-up people! That mean he
allowed to bring things to sell!

rows.label: tlk42100181_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Ahehem! From this day forth,
Magomago aspire to become merchant
just like Grampypon!
